    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained over the years. The exterior paint still shines beautifully, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front end and a few light scratches near the door handles consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, shifts smoothly, and all major electronics are fully functional, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
