    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this ride, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in truly mint condition\u2014spotless inside and out, and it still has that fresh car feel. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy. If you're looking for a car that\u2019s been totally pampered and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
