      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade A80 Supra Turbo, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant. This example retains its factory-spec sequential twin-turbochargers and the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue, and the undercarriage is pristine, preserving the original double-wishbone geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential. All VIN tags are present on body panels, confirming an accident-free history. The forced induction system holds peak boost pressure with surgical precision, and the factory ECU remains untampered. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
